12. Functional Requirements Documentation
FR-01: User Registration

Users shall be able to create an account.

Acceptance Criteria:
User successfully registers with valid details.

FR-02: User Login

Users shall log in securely.

Acceptance Criteria:
System authenticates credentials correctly.

FR-03: Search Books

Users shall search books using keywords.

Acceptance Criteria:
Relevant books appear in results.

FR-04: View Book Details
Users shall view author, category, description.

Acceptance Criteria:
System displays accurate metadata.

FR-05: Access E-Books
Users shall read/download books.

Acceptance Criteria:
Book opens without errors.

FR-06: Upload Books
Admin shall upload e-books.

Acceptance Criteria:
Book appears in library.

FR-07: Manage Books
Admin edits or deletes records.

Acceptance Criteria:
Changes reflect immediately.
